modShortDescription: Another JaxTeller718 mod! You don't have to go to the bird nests for eggs all the time. Look in those fridges. Eggs now appear in them!
modDescription:
Another JaxTeller718 mod! You don’t have to go to the bird nests for [eggs](https://7daystodiemods.com/food-mods/) all the time. Out of birds nests? Look in those fridges. Eggs now appear in them!

[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/JaxTeller718/JaxTeller718_Modlets_Stable/tree/master/JaxTeller718_EggsInFridges)

If you appreciate JaxTeller718’s work here feel free to use this [donate link](https://www.paypal.me/FrankCirabisiJr) to show support.

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/8098-jaxteller718-modlet-collection/).

**Credits:** [JaxTeller718](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/jaxteller718/)
